{"tid":2040823,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有BNO 有被人影過大頭應該即走","createTime":"2020-05-28T23:49:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-29T03:57:24.000Z","uid":259120,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"bac2d95c2b68683bf9e5ec6938c27be64c6190b6","tid":2040823,"uid":259120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T23:49:31.000Z","msg":"國安局已經拍板成立<br />\n呢個擺明係一個桂民海式捉人酷刑審犯機構<br />\n所以英國立即用行政方式改BNO 逗留限制<br />\n好大可能係覺得局勢會惡劣得好快，<br />\n等唔切9 月BNO 平權bill<br />\n而就算平權bill 提前審議，<br />\n開放BNO/BC 畀97後出世既年輕人<br />\n到時實在有太多人需要走<br />\n所以宜家先作分流<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>到時你唔好同班細路爭機位，船位<br />\nYou are warned</strong></span>"},{"pid":"c752c083e159127ba808d7a0ccc9a30d380ba225","tid":2040823,"uid":62891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T23:51:22.000Z","msg":"不了"},{"pid":"76e9ebdfe7081a58f29a09cb8594d05ef4df2597","tid":2040823,"uid":122233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T23:54:55.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"63064ce332d33e5e8f7698686702cea0b6314f37","tid":2040823,"uid":38518,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T00:10:47.000Z","msg":"仲未實行架"},{"pid":"c6df9d6f5d38730dbe35e16388a87106480d8887","tid":2040823,"uid":181502,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T00:12:09.000Z","msg":"有BNO喺連登講過粗口都要走🙏🏻🙏🏻"},{"pid":"95fddc558d0e56f222950fea75df1bb7aa13dc76","tid":2040823,"uid":146030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T00:19:50.000Z","msg":"exactly"},{"pid":"73311a90a7ce55dbe98ddff949536506be8de2f3","tid":2040823,"uid":8681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63064ce332d33e5e8f7698686702cea0b6314f37","tid":2040823,"uid":38518,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T00:10:47.000Z","msg":"仲未實行架"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T00:23:21.000Z","msg":"實行先走走得切？"},{"pid":"34e9bbba93988c061a8427d3a07a3f65152625c8","tid":2040823,"uid":38518,"like":